  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0cm 5.75pt 0cm 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor resemble beetles or cockroaches of earth in
  origin. Smaller than average dark skinned insectoids. </p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor rarely communicate with others and seem to v=
alue
  spreading themselves out to other planets above all else. </p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Yor are not very intelligent but work well as a grou=
p.
  They do not have a concept of copyright or patent, stealing ideas is
  acceptable, advancement in technology comes about because of a common dri=
ve
  towards their own races power not personal gain. </p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor have years of knowledge of phaser beam techn=
ology
  and have adapted their phaser technology to work on star fighter scale.<s=
pan
  style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>The Yor Stinger Beam gains more =
range
  than comparable Phasers, allowing them to strike first before the enemy h=
as
  realised they are upon them.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The Yor can be found in the driest deserts, their ha=
bitats
  built upon the sand and crawling with Yor who do not seem to mind
  overpopulation others would find uncomfortable.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-bottom:8.0pt'>The Yor preferred weap=
on is
  the Phaser and they focus have a Balanced approach to Energy Research.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><i style=3D'mso-bidi-font-style:normal'><o:p>&nbsp;<=
/o:p></i></p>
